name: 1ST SKETCH on iPad
description:
This is my first sketch using iPad that I was able to bought  almost a month on HEN. Almost 6 years of drawing and illustrating on my phone, no plan to stop, until this milestone happened. And then, surprisingly, new dreams and visions come along the way.

Thank you for the rightful and respectful collectors, as always. And to my co-artists in this space.

Love you all,

-Jakestudyos
